**Field options read format**
```js
{
    dateFormat: {
        name: 'local' | 'friendly' | 'us' | 'european' | 'iso',
        // Will correspond to name (e.g. {name: 'friendly', format: 'LL'}
        format: 'l' | 'LL' | 'M/D/YYYY' | 'D/M/YYYY' | 'YYYY-MM-DD',
    }
}
